    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Music by TeknoAxe.<br><br>Unleash cosmic annihilation as a goat armed with a demon gun.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Cultist Astronaut</i> is a 2D action-platformer set in a galaxy where cults wage apocalyptic wars. Invade planets, conquer rival cults, and absorb souls. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834700/extras/1e05dde907830c05fb961fe36f8d9ea9.avif?t=1768938535\" width=580 height=420 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Platforming with air control, wall slides, and double jumps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight cults in any order and unlock their weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Absorb souls to power up and unleash Soul Drain attacks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834700/extras/b8b83ebaa1a3bf04f814534fd5bc8047.avif?t=1768938535\" width=630 height=202 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Cults of the Galaxy</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Excoria</strong>: Home of the Flayed. Miners who flayed themselves to cure Rockskin disease now worship the Skinless One. Their weapons are razors; their cure is agony.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sludge Haven</strong>: Infested by the Imposters. Worm-like mimics who steal corpses and personalities to feel whole. Fight Nobodies, Somebodies, Anybody, and Everybody.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>More cults await:</strong> cyborg, radioactive corporations, mummified death cults, and spider angels.</p></li></ul>",
